{"tid":250512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（港男福音）2cm的驕傲　奈米屌男用技巧勝過30cm","createTime":"2017-05-20T06:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T08:04:22.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"118d86d02089551af6d1cde59138330e6e15ddf5","tid":250512,"uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/143817_50d5b369df9bceea4bbae2e2e65174d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F143817_50d5b369df9bceea4bbae2e2e65174d5.jpg&h=eb2a67b0&s={SIZE}\" />2cm的驕傲　奈米屌男用技巧勝過30cm<br />\n英國50歲奈米屌男史密斯(Ant Smith)不怕與人分享自己奈米屌的故事與經歷，甚至為此感到自豪，他認為雞不在小，有技巧則靈，一樣能勝過30公分大鵰。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，史密斯接受節目訪問，他稱自己的陰莖尺寸大約只有2~3公分，勃起後也不過10公分，低於英國人平均的14公分。但史密斯不認為自己很「弱小」，也不認為要被貼上「奈米屌」的標籤，他甚至出書，希望讓一樣擁有奈米屌的男性鼓起勇氣，只要方法正確，奈米屌一樣能展雄風。史密斯說，讓奈米屌「放大」的方法有兩項，第一是不要過度增肥，這樣會讓生殖器容易變成「縮頭烏龜」。其二是在專業醫療監控之下，可使用陰莖牽引(traction)的助長裝置。<br />\n史密斯對於自己的奈米屌非常有信心，也強調他常常能讓自己的美妻嗨翻天。不過史密斯也承認，他並非從小就對自己的奈米屌有信心。他說奈米屌是天生的，他小時候確實被同學嘲笑，讓他一度很沒有自信，不敢做愛，直到21歲才敢破處。史密斯說，他的陰莖小到連保險套都套不住，然後又被灌輸陰莖要15~17公分才算「正常」。但當他年近30歲時，他終於「開竅」，領悟到雞不在短小，有技巧則靈，也鼓勵一樣有奈米屌的男性能勇敢面對。<br />\n台灣網友紛紛表示：「棒不在長，有技則靈，妹不在正，有騷則行。」、「能爽就好管他什麼屌。」、「10公分以下可以哭了。」、「軀不在寬，會轉則敏。」（<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170520/1122384/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170520%2F1122384%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5b370798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170520/1122384/</a><br />\n<br />\n短小精幹，說法無錯"},{"pid":"860a01e7880c3fe64569dbe31f5811131188bf19","tid":250512,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T06:39:56.000Z","msg":"眾多連登仔有福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4fd78737b7e5200c031749ac8b845fd1619bdf","tid":250512,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T06:40:58.000Z","msg":"2cm 都係21歲就破左處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6a0d75171afa30bc6e5300d1105440c337682e","tid":250512,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T06:41:31.000Z","msg":"10cm唔算短啦<br />\n當年文員仔7cm"},{"pid":"32a97883791c3e3f509d785c369e60a706da7214","tid":250512,"uid":78347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T06:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眾多連登仔有福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用得著咩"},{"pid":"8a0902dfa7284438e975426114288f768f7ac12a","tid":250512,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T06:41:45.000Z","msg":"點樣有技巧法呀?<br />\n快D教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5932a0f06d8063a6049b56f81919c007e203ec59","tid":250512,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"演技係禮貌既一種"},{"pid":"13787f6483bd5d0c001cfb5c17cf3fe87f42946d","tid":250512,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>眾多連登仔有福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用得著咩</blockquote><br />\n連登仔就算300cm未又係用黎痾尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4cfcdd96f2c2ef169f6c5b1f57eb5fb8ec0187","tid":250512,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>眾多連登仔有福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用得著咩</blockquote><br />\n連登仔就算300cm未又係用黎痾尿<img src=\"/assets